          "reviewBody": "Digusting school. Horrible infrastructure. Opportunities only given to studious students. Teachers are nagging you constantly to tie two braids with ribbons  even for seniors. If a girl dares to tie a single braid shes basically a slut. Scolding and screaming at children without any reason. No civic sense. Discrimination based on religion. No teacher is qualified . it's better to self study than go and listen to every single teacher simply reading out of the book and writing on the board. Some teachers even exercise physical abuse. Students are literally forced to attend school trips that cost 25000( they call parents every single day to send their child). Kids are infamous for misusing drugs and alchohol. Moreover the toilets are worse than third ac train compartments. There are only two western toilets and are usually clogged. On top of it all every single day we are made to sing and dance for atlest thirty minutes to jesus songs and then we must thank the entire pinto family as if they are jesus themselves. There are no facilities at all. No dance, music, yoga classes and sports period is only once a week with a horribly maintained ground which is always occupied and all girls are told to play on a narrow pathway. If u r selected for the hockey team only then do they prioritise you. Even most of the buses are in terrible condition with jammed windows and water leaking from roofs. Don't ruin your child's life please by sending them here I'm begging you. Your life will be made miserable.",
